A great function could be the possibility, at project administration level, to define the Workflow between issues, for example the PM can define a chained flow of different issues! example : Issue types ( requirement ), ( development ), ( Test ), ( implementation ), ( documentation ), ( Q&A ). with Parallel routing flow. The PM assigne the detailed business requirement specificatoin to a process manager, when it's resolved it goes to a predefined deveopment team ( Multiple assignement ), when it's solved automatically goes in 3 parallel phases ( test & implementation & documentation ) when all 3 issues are solved it goes to the Q & A.  We have done it at this moment trough a listener, added a java class and manipulating everytime manually a file property. An idea could be manage the file property with an XML file, create this file trough a xml workflow designer ( like reactor studio )and let it read by Jira.

