It would be nice if there was a quick way to determine what the current version of a project is.

One thing we've been doing manually is on the Project Title we put the current version in () i.e. (v.2.2.60).

This is a pain though, as we have several projects listed.  I know that projects may not have versions but if they do they could pull the last released version and stick it in the Project Title.

